00:21:20.720 --> 00:21:33.300
<v Trevor Manz>to sort of orient itself where you are inside the notebook, versus if I asked the agent, you know, we're focusing on this cell right now inside the notebook, the agent doesn't have to print off all the other cells into context, it can just focus on that one cell

